claim.claim-text:
10. The battery apparatus of claim 9, wherein the processor is further configured to:
estimate an open circuit voltage of the battery based on the surface SOC;
estimate an overpotential of the battery based on the SOC and the surface SOC;
estimate a voltage due to an ohmic resistance of the battery based on the measured current of the battery; and
estimate the terminal voltage based on the open circuit voltage, the overpotential, and the voltage due to the ohmic resistance.

17. The method of claim 13, further comprising:
estimating a first voltage based on the surface SOC;
estimating a second voltage based on the SOC and the surface SOC;
estimating a third voltage based on the measured current of the battery; and
estimating a terminal voltage of the battery based on the first voltage, the second voltage, and the third voltage.
